{"tid":496691,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡頓保：加比爾捷西斯插水勢停兩場","createTime":"2017-12-12T02:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T03:41:28.000Z","uid":333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6964dd71ab1323e4cd3440dc8d704edbaf32a5","tid":496691,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:48:14.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Wk6sw9ONsJJDxQCO8jxROozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=fc488de7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前英超球證卡頓保預計，曼城鋒將加比爾捷西斯將因插水行為被秋後算帳，料遭停賽兩場。<br />\n<br />\n周日曼徹斯特打吡戰的餘波，除了是「水樽門」外，還有加比爾捷西斯（Gabriel Jesus）被指在上半場與基斯史摩寧肩碰肩後卻倒下，雖然他沒有因此事得益，獲得12碼或導致球證向敵方出示黃牌，然而卡頓保相信，事件一樣會令加比爾面臨3人小組的裁決。<br />\n<br />\n卡頓保接受《泰晤士報》訪問時說：「在上半場所發生的事件，是加比爾捷西斯插水。我認為事件會受英超賽會調查，將會很有趣。那將由一名球證、一名前球員及一名前領隊組成的小組審視。球證將會同意那是插水，而最終裁決取決於後兩者，因為必須3:0的裁決才會發出停賽令。」<br />\n<br />\n曼城在周日這場大戰作客奧脫福贏2:1，在榜首領放11分。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"626dc78f768a67320a4430f58ebebeb59f27b1ed","tid":496691,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"卡頓保好多野講"},{"pid":"c2cb883d2308ecc04c2072478ac418e5e2d0c502","tid":496691,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卡頓保好多野講</blockquote><br />\n好似去左吹油王聯賽?"},{"pid":"802330c9b59ab14821f98346bc7c8a7a0f7dff29","tid":496691,"uid":112213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:11:12.000Z","msg":"咁靴里拉唔止黃牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2281bfc3fcf05afcc0ee6aec69bcb261744d98","tid":496691,"uid":37798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:11:45.000Z","msg":"呢下即場唔吹真係痴線"},{"pid":"3850bbf42715f79ead48665c66f0d8d9b6c2dcff","tid":496691,"uid":131176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁靴里拉唔止黃牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獌狗唔會有事,盧卡古踢人都無野"},{"pid":"6c2603fae1060546525ab280316607c487c57006","tid":496691,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>卡頓保好多野講</blockquote><br />\n好似去左吹油王聯賽?</blockquote><br />\n所以依家休季"},{"pid":"32fe0ad0f78f1874967c6373144b0389197f46b4","tid":496691,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:20:29.000Z","msg":"條垃圾呢排咁搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b76c7fdbc16ad3ead402ebbaeff53f35b5d45a","tid":496691,"uid":123243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"連反曼球証都咁講 插水狗節西斯停啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cb6373b6c04158fb04f8f95880f6048abe698d","tid":496691,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連反曼球証都咁講 插水狗節西斯停啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503e30611f82883a91a6b51f4c57b54af5e94d7f","tid":496691,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連反曼球証都咁講 插水狗節西斯停啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於敢上水"},{"pid":"88a5285665d1ad547df860aa77c3ecfbf7083115","tid":496691,"uid":34490,"